People ex rel. Wooster, Respondent, v. Maher, Mayor, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 14, 1892.) Application for mandamus by Benjamin W. Wooster against Edward A. Maher, as mayor of Albany.

Argued before Mayham, P. J., and Putnam and Herrick, JJ.

No opinion. Motion to correct decision by granting relator costs, granted. See 19 N. Y. Supp. 758.
